OL,3,CPlans show #60m 'gap' in Reform
OL,4,Ccouncil's budget even with council tax
OL,5,Cincrease
OL,7,FReform UK's flagship local authority's
OL,8,Fdebt will increase by tens of millions
OL,9,Fof pounds, even if it puts up council
OL,10,Ftax by the maximum possible amount,
OL,11,Faccording to a leaked forecast of next
OL,12,Fyear's finances.
OL,14,FKent County Council (KCC) was won by
OL,15,FReform at local elections in May, when
OL,16,Ftheir candidates promised to cut
OL,17,Fcouncil spending and keep taxes low.
