OL,5,Cincrease
OL,7,FSoon after taking power, the
OL,8,Fadministration set up an Elon Musk-
OL,9,Fstyle savings unit called the
OL,10,FDepartment of Local Government
OL,11,FEfficiency (DOLGE).
OL,13,FA leaked slideshow for opposition
OL,14,Fcouncillors shows there is a #60
OL,15,Fmillion gap in KCC's finances for 2026-
OL,16,F27.
OL,18,FUnder the plans for next year set out
OL,19,Fby the previous Tory administration,
OL,20,Fthat unresolved gap was #20.1 million.
