OL,3,CPlans show #60m 'gap' in Reform
OL,4,Ccouncil's budget even with council tax
OL,5,Cincrease
OL,7,FThat plan, shown to a councillor in
OL,8,Fmid-November, also currently includes
OL,9,Fa full 5% increase in council tax, to
OL,10,Fkeep the gap at #60 million.
OL,12,FFor a band D property in Kent, this
OL,13,Fwould mean an increase of #84.56 per
OL,14,Fyear from #1,691.19 in 2025-26 to
OL,15,F#1775.75.
