OL,7,FIn a full council meeting at Sessions
OL,8,FHouse, in Maidstone, on Thursday,
OL,9,Fformer Reform councillor Bill Barrett
OL,10,Fsaid he had been told "the gap" may
OL,11,Fincrease further, up to #100 million,
OL,12,Fin the new year.
OL,14,FThe current plan does not factor in
OL,15,Fmoney KCC will receive from the UK
OL,16,FGovernment thanks to the fair funding
OL,17,Freview which KCC leader Linden
OL,18,FKemkaran has said will provide them
OL,19,Fwith an 8% increase in overall funding.
