OL,7,FHowever, even if that significant
OL,8,Fincrease in funding plugs the gap,
OL,9,FReform's new plan for 2026-27 will
OL,10,Fstill see council expenditure increase
OL,11,Fby #31 million from what the previous
OL,12,FTory administration had planned.
OL,14,FIt is understood that the majority of
OL,15,Fthat excess spending is on the
OL,16,Fincreased price of adult social care.
