OL,7,FLabour MP for Dartford Jim Dickson
OL,8,Fsaid providers of some elements of
OL,9,Fadult social care have been told their
OL,10,Ffunding will be "hugely cut" in three
OL,11,Fmonths, including "navigation and
OL,12,Fwellbeing services" which provide old
OL,13,Fand vulnerable adults "on the edge of
OL,14,Fcare" with contact and support,
OL,15,Fwithout a full care package.
OL,17,FA study by Involve, an organisation
OL,18,Fproviding that type of care, found
OL,19,Fthat it led to "significant
OL,20,Freductions" in A&E attendance and need
OL,21,Ffor acute care.
