OL,7,F"Kent are obviously claiming that this
OL,8,Fis an efficiency and something that
OL,9,Fthey can do without huge service
OL,10,Feffect but that's quite clearly
OL,11,Fwrong," Mr Dickson said.
OL,13,FAt Sessions House on Thursday, leader
OL,14,Fof the opposition Antony Hook said the
OL,15,Ffair funding review was a "sticking
OL,16,Fplaster on a gaping wound".
OL,18,FThe Liberal Democrat councillor added:
OL,19,F"In the absence of a budget,
OL,20,Feverything is in danger.
