OL,7,F"Everything is in danger from a Reform
OL,8,Fadministration that doesn't value our
OL,9,Fpublic services, doesn't value the
OL,10,Fpeople we work for and certainly
OL,11,Fdoesn't value residents independently."
OL,13,FThere was clear frustration among all
OL,14,Fthe opposition groups, that a draft of
OL,15,FKCC's budget is yet to be provided.
OL,17,FThe leaked briefing is one option for
OL,18,Fthe Reform administration, who are now
OL,19,Fexpected to present their draft budget
OL,20,Fat the start of January.
